data.title: Travis Barker & Rita Ora Dating, Share Love for Punk Rock
data.meta_description: News broke Thursday that Rita Ora and Travis Barker are now dating and the Blink-182 drummer isn't shying from talking about the new relationship.
data.text:
News broke Thursday that Rita Ora and Travis Barker are now dating and the Blink-182 drummer isn’t shying from talking about the new relationship.

Travis Barker on New Lineup Post-Tom DeLonge Exit: ‘It’s Definitely a Great Feeling’

On Thursday night, Barker was at Knott’s Berry Farm’s Knott’s Scary Farm opening in Buena Park, Calif., and asked by E! News where Ora was.

Without any sort of hesitation, Barker said Ora was probably coming later. When prompted, he said they would “possibly” be dressing up for Halloween together.

Rita Ora Talks New Album, ’50 Shades of Grey’ & More at iHeartRadio Music Fest 2015

He continued, on his own accord, “We actually share a lot of the same tastes in music. Little did I know that she likes punk rock a lot. I love that. I was raised on it.”

The couple first met a couple weeks ago at the Power 106 All-Star basketball game in Los Angeles, Barker’s rep confirmed with TMZ.
